sqrt
1.4142135623730951

# DOCS_TEST: example_005

query
SELECT (m[1]).map_entries()
FROM (VALUES ([MAP {'hello': 42}, MAP {'world': 42}])) t(m);
----
map_entries
<slt:ignore>

